How to Join:

    1. Go to #IoTChat on Twitter Thursday at 1pm PT
    2. @OReillySolid will post 12 questions about IoT topics, one every
       few minutes, labeled Q1, Q2, Q3, etc.
    3. Anwer the questions that are the most interesting to you, labeling
       them for the corresponding question: (A1, A2, A3, etc.).
    4. Make sure all comments, replies, or retweets include the hashtag
       #IoTChat so everyone can see your tweets.
    5. At the end of the #IoTChat, one random participant will win a free
       prize announced from @OReillySolid

   Like a party, the Tweet Chat will move quickly and be done before you
   know it. It's always a lot of fun and a great way to learn, brainstorm,
   and make new contacts.

   See you on Twitter May 15th.





